    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4568670/" class="title-link">一趟列车，一群人，一段历史，一个民族……</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4568670"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2738148/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
